title: Still making a logo, still needing feedback
content:
I post this only to tell you that i have uploaded a new version of the logo i'm currently working on.

[http://typophile.com/node/33235](http://web.archive.org/web/20131018052553/http:/typophile.com/node/33235 "http://typophile.com/node/33235")

Was this rude? starting a new thread to call attention to an old one? hope not. If so, i did it only because your feedback is so useful.

thanks,

alex
